data.value: The Porsche 911 is a two-door, rear-engined sports car that was first introduced in 1964 by Porsche AG of Stuttgart, Germany.The 911 has been continuously updated over the years, but its basic concept has remained the same.The car's rear wing and rear-engine layout give it better traction and balance.making it one of the best-selling sports cars of alL time.
